data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a generous 2-acre parcel of serene countryside in the heart of the county. This property offers a delightful blend of modern comforts, spacious living, and outdoor amenities, making it the perfect retreat for those seeking a peaceful, rural lifestyle. This home boasts four well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for your family or guests. The open split floor plan ensures privacy and convenience for all occupants.  The heart of the home is the inviting eat-in kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances and convenient bar seating. It's the perfect place for preparing delicious meals and entertaining friends and family.  Conveniently located just off the kitchen, the laundry room offers practicality and easy access for your daily chores.  The spacious master suite is a true oasis. The en-suite bathroom features double sinks, a separate shower, and a luxurious soaking tub. The master bedroom also boasts a large walk-in closet, providing plenty of storage space for your wardrobe and personal belongings.  From the kitchen, step out onto the covered patio, where you can enjoy the tranquility of your expansive backyard. In the front of the house, a welcoming porch is the perfect spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation.  The property features a 2-car metal detached garage with shelves and a dedicated workspace for DIY enthusiasts or those in need of extra storage space. Additionally, there is a metal carport for more covered parking or storage, ensuring your vehicles and equipment are protected. For even more storage solutions, a brand-new storage building is also included on the property. With 2 acres of land at your disposal, you have plenty of room to explore your outdoor interests, whether it's gardening, playing, or simply taking in the beautiful county scenery.  This property offers a delightful mix of modern amenities and country living. It's an ideal home for those who value space, comfort, and the tranquility of rural living, all within a short drive to town. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your home. Schedule a viewing today to experience its charm for yourself.
